pageContext.claim: “[Beto] said started saying I was born -- I was born to do this. I was born to run for President. I said he's not going to last very long and about two weeks later, it was over.”
pageContext.analysis: Beto O'Rourke made this comment in a March 2019 Vanity Fair article. After the article was released, he joined the field of 2020 Democratic contenders. He dropped out several months — not weeks — later.
